Installation of Nmap in linux: 

commands of installing nmap from source code full powerful version
	$ svn
	$ svn help
	$ apt install libssl-dev autoconf make g++ subversion
	$ svn co https://svn.nmap.org/nmap
	$ ./configure --help
	$ ./configure
	$ make
	
	
	if after "make" command if you get error type command
		$ sudo pip install setuptools==62.0.0
		
	$ make install
